name: Gerard Dacudao
text: Roy, the only difference between you and them is that they can pay many employees to do exactly what you did.  But the truth is already out there.  You yourself saw it. 38% was for Du30 in your homegrown survey.    At isa pa.  May seryosong problema, may conflict. Ang may ari ng SWS at PA ay Cojuanco at Mangahas na Tito ni Grace Poe!  I'd rather believe you than believe PA and SWS!
